underlying_goal: Find and fix any content overflow issues in a Slidev presentation.
primary_success: Successfully used a subagent to analyze a PDF, correctly identified a content overflow issue on a specific page, and applied multiple targeted CSS and content condensation techniques to fix it.
brief_summary: Using the `/fix-slide` command, the agent exported a presentation to PDF and used a subagent to find a content overflow issue on page 10. The agent then located the corresponding markdown and applied several layout and content adjustments to resolve the overflow.
